</a></li>\n\t<li id=\"menu-item-73\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-73\"><a href=\"https://cml.ics.uci.edu/aiml/ml-reading-group/\">ML Reading Group</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li id=\"menu-item-222\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom current-menu-ancestor current-menu-parent menu-item-has-children menu-item-222\"><a>Education &#038; Resources</a>\n<ul class=\"sub-menu\">\n\t<li id=\"menu-item-227\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-227\"><a href=\"https://cml.ics.uci.edu/courses/\">Courses</a></li>\n\t<li id=\"menu-item-221\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page current-menu-item page_item page-item-162 current_page_item menu-item-221\"><a href=\"https://cml.ics.uci.edu/books/\" aria-current=\"page\">Books</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li id=\"menu-item-81\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-81\"><a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~mlearn/MLRepository.html\">UCI Machine Learning Archive</a></li>\n<li id=\"menu-item-87\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-87\"><a href=\"https://cml.ics.uci.edu/sponsors-funding/\">Sponsors &#038; Funding</a></li>\n<li id=\"menu-item-86\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-86\"><a href=\"https://cml.ics.uci.edu/subscribe/\">Subscribe to CML List</a></li>\n</ul></div>\t\t</nav><!-- #site-navigation -->\n\t</header><!-- #masthead -->\n\n\r\n\t<div id=\"primary\" class=\"content-area\">\r\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"site-content\" role=\"main\">\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n<article id=\"post-162\" class=\"post-162 page type-page status-publish hentry\">\r\n\t<header class=\"entry-header\">\r\n\t\t<h1 class=\"entry-title\">Books </h1>\r\n\t</header><!-- .entry-header -->\r\n\r\n\t<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"book\">\n<div class=\"book-thumb\"><img src='http://cml.ics.uci.edu//wp-content/cml/uploads/constraint.jpg' alt='Cover'></div>\n<div class=\"info\">\n<div class=\"title\"><a href='http://www.ics.uci.edu/~dechter/books/index.html'>Constraint Processing</a></div>\n<div class=\"authors\">Rina Dechter</div>\n<div class=\"publisher\">Morgan Kauffman </div>\n<div class=\"quote\">\n&#8220;This book provides a comprehensive and much needed introduction to the field by one of its foremost experts. It is beautifully written and presents a unifying framework capturing a wide range of techniques for processing symbolic, numerical, and probabilistic information.&#8221; </p>\n<div class=\"quote-attr\">&#8211;Bart Selman, Cornell University</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><br class=\"clear\" /></p>\n<div class=\"book\">\n<div class=\"book-thumb\"><img src='http://cml.ics.uci.edu//wp-content/cml/uploads/modeling.jpg' alt='Cover'></div>\n<div class=\"info\">\n<div class=\"title\"><a href='http://www.igb.uci.edu/~pfbaldi/?page=books#Modeling%20the%20Internet%20and%20the%20Web.%20Probabilistic%20Methods%20and%20Algorithms'>Modeling the Internet and the Web. Probabilistic Methods and Algorithms</a></div>\n<div class=\"authors\">Pierre Baldi, Paolo Frasconi, and Padhraic Smyth</div>\n<div class=\"publisher\">Wiley </div>\n<div class=\"quote\">\n&#8220;This book provides an extremely useful introduction to the intellectually stimulating problems of data mining electronic business.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"quote-attr\">&#8212; Andreas S. Weigend (Chief Scientist, Amazon.com)</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><br class=\"clear\" /></p>\n<div class=\"book\">\n<div class=\"book-thumb\"><img src='http://cml.ics.uci.edu//wp-content/cml/uploads/bioinformatics.jpg' alt='Cover'></div>\n<div class=\"info\">\n<div class=\"title\"><a href='http://www.igb.uci.edu/~pfbaldi/?page=books#Bioinformatics'>Bioinformatics: the Machine Learning Approach (2nd ed.)</a></div>\n<div class=\"authors\">Pierre Baldi and S\u00c3\u00b8ren Brunak</div>\n<div class=\"publisher\">MIT Press</div>\n<div class=\"quote\">\n&#8220;This is a very good book, written with a high level of erudition and insight.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"quote-attr\">&#8212; Gustavo A. Stolovitzky, Physics Today </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><br class=\"clear\" /></p>\n<div class=\"book\">\n<div class=\"book-thumb\"><img src='http://cml.ics.uci.edu//wp-content/cml/uploads/mining.jpg' alt='Cover'></div>\n<div class=\"info\">\n<div class=\"title\"><a href='http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/026208290X/qid%3D1049992810/sr%3D11-1/ref%3Dsr%5F11%5F1/103-8656473-5759037'>Principles of Data Mining (Adaptive Computation and Machine Learning)</a></div>\n<div class=\"authors\">David J. Hand, Heikki Mannila, and Padhraic Smyth</div>\n<div class=\"publisher\">MIT Press</div>\n<div class=\"quote\">\n&#8220;Principles of Data Mining is a well-thought-out lucid introduction to data mining principles and techniques that is a pleasure to read. It would be a worthy addition to your bookshelf.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"quote-attr\">&#8211;Ashish P. Sanil, National Institute of Statistical Sciences, from the Journal of the American Statistical Association</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><br class=\"clear\" /></p>\n<div class=\"book\">\n<div class=\"book-thumb\"><img src='http://cml.ics.uci.edu//wp-content/cml/uploads/bayesian.jpg' alt='Cover'></div>\n<div class=\"info\">\n<div class=\"title\"><a href='http://www.stat.columbia.edu/~gelman/book/'>Bayesian Data Analysis</a></div>\n<div class=\"authors\">Andrew Gelman, John B. Carlin, Hal S. Stern, and Donald B. Rubin</div>\n<div class=\"publisher\">CRC Press </div>\n<div class=\"quote\">\n&#8220;Bayesian Data Analysis is easily the most comprehensive, scholarly, and thoughtful book on the subject, and I think will do much to promote the use of Bayesian methods.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"quote-attr\">&#8211;Prof. David Blackwell, Department of Statistics, University of California, Berkeley</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><br class=\"clear\" /></p>\n<div class=\"book\">\n<div class=\"book-thumb\"><img src='http://cml.ics.uci.edu//wp-content/cml/uploads/shattered.jpg' alt='Cover'></div>\n<div class=\"info\">\n<div class=\"title\"><a href='http://www.igb.uci.edu/~pfbaldi/?page=books#The%20Shattered%20Self'>The Shattered Self &#8211; The End of Natural Evolution</a></div>\n<div class=\"authors\">Pierre Baldi</div>\n<div class=\"publisher\">MIT Press </div>\n<div class=\"quote\">\n&#8220;What we will become remains intriguing and ominous, making this probing book a valuable contribution to thinking about our future.&#8221; </p>\n<div class=\"quote-attr\">&#8212; Steven R. Quartz, American Scientist</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><br class=\"clear\" /></p>\n<div class=\"book\">\n<div class=\"book-thumb\"><img src='http://cml.ics.uci.edu//wp-content/cml/uploads/microarrays.jpg' alt='Cover'></div>\n<div class=\"info\">\n<div class=\"title\"><a href='http://www.igb.uci.edu/~pfbaldi/?page=books#DNA%20Microarrays'>DNA Microarrays and Gene Regulation</a></div>\n<div class=\"authors\">Pierre Baldi and G. Wesley Hatfield</div>\n<div class=\"publisher\">Cambridge University Press</div>\n<div class=\"quote\">\n&#8220;Writing a book such as this was a challenging remit and one that the authors have achieved with great success.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"quote-attr\">&#8212; Human Genomics</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><br class=\"clear\" /></p>\n<div class=\"book\">\n<div class=\"book-thumb\"><img src='http://cml.ics.uci.edu//wp-content/cml/uploads/reasoning.jpg' alt='Cover'></div>\n<div class=\"info\">\n<div class=\"title\"><a href='http://www.morganclaypool.com/doi/abs/10.2200/S00529ED1V01Y201308AIM023'>Reasoning with Probabilistic and Deterministic Graphical Models: Exact Algorithms</a></div>\n<div class=\"authors\">Rina Dechter</div>\n<div class=\"publisher\">Morgan &#038; Claypool</div>\n<div class=\"quote\">\n<div class=\"quote-attr\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- .entry-content -->\r\n\t</article><!-- #post-## -->\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t</div><!-- #content -->\r\n\r\n\t</div><!-- #primary -->\r\n\r\n\t<div id=\"secondary\" class=\"widget-area\" role=\"complementary\">\n\t\t\t\t<aside id=\"search-2\" class=\"widget widget_search\">\t<form method=\"get\" id=\"searchform\" class=\"searchform\" action=\"https://cml.ics.uci.edu/\" role=\"search\">\n\t\t<label for=\"s\" class=\"screen-reader-text\">Search</label>\n\t\t<input type=\"search\" class=\"field\" name=\"s\" value=\"\" id=\"s\" placeholder=\"Search &hellip;\" />\n\t\t<input type=\"submit\" class=\"submit\" id=\"searchsubmit\" value=\"Search\" />\n\t</form>\n</aside>\t</div><!-- #secondary -->\n\r\n</div><!-- #page -->\r\n\r\n<footer id=\"colophon\" class=\"site-footer\" role=\"contentinfo\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0;\">(c) 2015 <a href=\"http://cml.ics.uci.edu\">Center for Machine Learning and Intelligent Systems</a>\r\n\t<div class=\"site-info\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://wordpress.org/\" rel=\"generator\">WordPress</a>/<a href=\"http://www.wpzoom.com/\">BonPress</a>\r\n\t</div><!-- .site-info -->\r\n</footer><!-- #colophon -->\r\n\r\n<script type='text/javascript' src='https://cml.ics.uci.edu/wp-content/cml/themes/bonpress-wpcom/js/navigation.js?ver=20120206'></script>\n<script type='text/javascript' src='https://cml.ics.uci.edu/wp-content/cml/themes/bonpress-wpcom/js/skip-link-focus-fix.js?ver=20130115'></script>\n<script type='text/javascript' src='https://cml.ics.uci.edu/wp-includes/js/wp-embed.min.js?ver=5.2.3'></script>\n\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n", "encoding": "ISO-8859-1"}